HTML5 Voice

A Simple Client-Server project to allow groups of people to talk to each other using new HTML5 Audio Recording APIs.

The Server is written in python and uses Twisted/AutoBahn to provide the service.

The Client is a JavaScript HTML5 application.

-- Client --

Be sure to npm-install the client requirements and run the gulp file.

-- Server -- 

Install the server requirements (Twisted, AutoBahn, etc.) and run server.py